{
  "text": "To restore the hologram obtained from the optical scanning holography, we need the focal distance of hologram. To know the focal depth, some researcher proposed the conventional imaging filtering [CITATION_1] , the auto-focusing technique based on the Wigner analysis [CITATION_2] , axis transform method [CITATION_3] , and so on. Unfortunately, these method are time consuming and difficult for real-time reconstruction because of the post-processing of hologram image.",
  "citation_candidates": [
